UID:7Z_to6UWVLdN4qjvph_s6
SUMMARY:Restoration Event with Leave No Trace
DTSTAMP:20260410T044137Z
DTSTART:20260411T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Leave No Trace and Green Issaquah for a family-friendly fu
	n volunteer day. Volunteers will work on projects including mulching\, rem
	oving trash\, and removing invasive plants from Confluence Park. Registrat
	ion is required: bit.ly/leavenotrace\\_restoration Leave No Trace is non-p
	rofit organization dedicated to protecting the outdoors \\(parks\, trails\
	, and public lands\\) through science-based education that encourages resp
	onsible recreation.  Along with 11 other cities\, Leave No Trace has selec
	ted Issaquah as one of its 2026 Spotlights Cities. This program in partner
	ship with Green Issaquah will bring three days of education\, outreach\, a
	nd restoration to parks and open spaces in the city!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6
	amcity.com/events/#/details/restoration-event-with-leave-no-trace/18529112
	/2026-04-11T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/restoration-event-with-le
	ave-no-trace/18529112/2026-04-11T00
