DTSTAMP:20260410T044137Z
DTSTART:20260411T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Gear up for Baby Rave by transforming everyday items into vibra
	nt wearable works of art with guidance from teaching artist\, Claudia Vill
	alobos! Upcycle materials including cardboard\, fabric scraps\, and repurp
	osed embellishments to design wings\, crowns\, skirts and other wearable p
	ieces that sparkle\, reflect light\, and show off your family's creativity
	. Ideal for kids and grown-ups to create together. Then spend your afterno
	on with your family exploring art and the natural environment. This progra
	m takes place outside at the Olympic Sculpture Park on the covered north t
	errace of the PACCAR Pavilion. Walk-ins welcome on a first-come\, first-se
