BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:cpvjoCncAt67K85lRmd2f
SUMMARY:Glass-school tours
DTSTAMP:20260410T044139Z
DTSTART:20260422T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Stanwood (54 miles N)\n\nWatch hot glass demonstrations\, meet 
	the artists\, take a tour of the campus founded by Dale Chihuly\, and shop
	 for glass art during Spring Tours at Pilchuk Glass School\, 1201 316th St
	. NW in Stanwood. [Click all of the ticket buttons to see all available ti
	meslots.]\n\nhttps://www.pilchuck.org/event/tours\n\nFrom Events12 Seattle
